                  <AccordionItem question="How do themes work?">
                    Apply <code>data-theme="dark"</code> or <code
                      >data-theme="brand"</code
                    > to any section or component. All semantic CSS variables cascade
                    automatically to children.
                  </AccordionItem>
                  <AccordionItem question="Does the accordion use GSAP?">
                    Yes — height animations use <code>gsap.fromTo</code> for smooth
                    open/close. If GSAP is unavailable it falls back to <code
                      >display: block/none</code
                    >.
